graph TB
    Client([Client App]) --> LB[Load Balancer]
    LB --> Gateway[LiteLLM Gateway]
    
    Gateway --> RateLimit[Rate Limiter<br/>20/min per user]
    RateLimit --> ExactCache{Exact Cache<br/>Redis}
    
    ExactCache -->|HIT| Response([Response])
    ExactCache -->|MISS| CB[Circuit Breaker]
    
    CB --> Primary
    CB -->|Primary DOWN| Backup
    CB -->|Both DOWN| Emergency
    
    subgraph Primary [Primary - OpenAI]
        GPT4o[GPT-4o / GPT-4o-mini]
    end
    
    subgraph Backup [Backup - Anthropic]
        Claude[Claude Sonnet / Haiku]
    end
    
    subgraph Emergency [Emergency - Local]
        Llama[Llama-3 via Ollama<br/>Self-hosted]
    end
    
    GPT4o --> Retry{Retry Logic}
    Claude --> Retry
    Llama --> Retry
    
    Retry -->|Success| Log
    Retry -->|Fail after 3x| NextProvider[Try Next Provider]
    NextProvider --> CB
    
    Log[Audit Log<br/>Every call tracked] --> Monitor[Monitor Dashboard]
    
    subgraph Monitor Dashboard
        Latency[p50/p95/p99 Latency]
        Errors[Error Rate per Provider]
        Cost[Cost per Provider]
        Health[Provider Health %]
    end
    
    Monitor --> Response
    
    subgraph Retry Logic Detail
        R1[Attempt 1 → wait 1s]
        R2[Attempt 2 → wait 2s + jitter]
        R3[Attempt 3 → wait 4s + jitter]
        R1 --> R2 --> R3
    end

    style Gateway fill:#1f6feb,color:#fff
    style CB fill:#d29922,color:#fff
    style RateLimit fill:#8957e5,color:#fff
    style Primary fill:#3fb950,color:#000
    style Backup fill:#d29922,color:#000
    style Emergency fill:#da3633,color:#fff
    style Log fill:#3fb950,color:#fff
